description: Everyone who has ever roamed through any of Radcliffe’s farmer’s markets is familiar with Chef Maria and the amazingly delicious Mediterranean meals you can find at her food truck, Gyros Express. For 16 years, she and her talented team have been providing the hungry people on the streets the tastiest variety of authentic soups, salads, gyros, and other hot wraps that fresh, healthy, and ready to enjoy!
name: Gyros Express
